#

Spicy Garlic Pickles

10 min
$5
15 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 8

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-CalorieGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

QuickSnackTangy

Description

Crunchy and zesty pickles with a spicy kick and a garlicky aroma, perfect as a snack or a side dish.

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 4 medium
  • garlic cloves: 6, smashed
  • red pepper flakes: 1 tablespoon
  • white vinegar: 2 cups
  • water: 1 cup
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 2 tablespoons
  • dill sprigs: 4 sprigs
